    {
      "instruction": "<p>Now, let’s get started!</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>quick cook spaghetti </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> then bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>spaghetti</strong> for 2-3 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>spaghetti</strong>, reserving a cup of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1700484085896-x200.jpg",
