    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the breadcrumbs are browning, chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>in 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[60ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[75ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong>, then stir in your <strong>creamy single soy</strong>– this is your<strong> creamy stock</strong></p>",
