    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>creamy stock </strong>and <strong>cooked spaghetti </strong>to the softened tomatoes and cook for 2-3 min, or until thickened to a double cream-like consistency</p>",
